## 🎨 UI Component Guidelines

### Platform-Agnostic Components (packages/ui)

**Goal**: Components should work on both web and mobile with minimal platform-specific code.

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: Conditional rendering for platform differences
import { Platform } from "react-native";

export function SessionCard({ session }: Props) {
  const Wrapper = Platform.OS === "web" ? "div" : View;
  
  return (
    <Wrapper>
      <Text>{session.title}</Text>
    </Wrapper>
  );
}
```

### Styling Strategy

**Web (apps/web)**:
```css
/* Use CSS variables for theming */
:root {
  --color-primary: #6366f1;
  --spacing-md: 1rem;
}

.session-card {
  padding: var(--spacing-md);
  background: var(--color-primary);
}
```

**Mobile (apps/mobile)**:
```typescript
// Use StyleSheet.create for performance
import { StyleSheet } from "react-native";

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  card: {
    padding: 16,
    backgroundColor: "#6366f1",
  },
});
```

