## 🧪 Testing Guidelines

### Test File Naming
```
ComponentName.tsx
ComponentName.test.tsx   // Unit tests
ComponentName.spec.tsx   // Integration tests
```

### Testing Library Preferences
- **Web**: `@testing-library/react` + Vitest
- **Mobile**: `@testing-library/react-native` + Jest
- **E2E**: Playwright (web) / Detox (mobile)

### Test Coverage Goals
| Layer | Target | Priority |
|-------|--------|----------|
| Services | 90%+ | Critical |
| Hooks | 80%+ | High |
| Utils | 95%+ | High |
| Components | 60%+ | Medium |

