## 📚 Key Commands

```bash
# Development
pnpm dev                              # Start all dev servers
pnpm --filter @tt-platform/web dev    # Web only
pnpm --filter @tt-platform/mobile start # Mobile only

# Build
pnpm build                            # Build all packages
pnpm type-check                       # Type check all packages

# Testing
pnpm test                             # Run all tests
pnpm --filter @tt-platform/shared test # Test shared package

# Firebase
cd functions && pnpm deploy           # Deploy Cloud Functions
firebase emulators:start              # Local Firebase emulators

# Mobile
pnpm --filter @tt-platform/mobile android  # Run on Android
pnpm --filter @tt-platform/mobile ios      # Run on iOS
eas build -p android                  # Production build (Android)
```

